description: Start importing bulk data into an ACTIVE data store. The import job imports DICOM P10 files found in the S3 prefix specified by the inputS3Uri parameter. The import job stores processing results in the file specified by the outputS3Uri parameter.

parameters.name: dataAccessRoleArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role that grants permission to access medical imaging resources.

parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: A unique identifier for API idempotency. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: inputS3Uri
parameters.description: The input prefix path for the S3 bucket that contains the DICOM files to be imported.

parameters.name: outputS3Uri
parameters.description: The output prefix of the S3 bucket to upload the results of the DICOM import job.

nested_items.name: submittedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the import job was submitted.
